snippet: Rafael Nadal reached his first quarterfinal since capturing the French Open in June with a 6-3, 6-4 win over a qualifier, Peter Gojowczyk, at the China Open, then blasted the choice of tennis balls at the tournament.
abstract: Rafael Nadal defeats Peter Gojowczyk at the China Open, reaching his first quarterfinal since capturing the French Open in June.
lead_paragraph: Rafael Nadal reached his first quarterfinal since capturing the French Open in June with a 6-3, 6-4 win over a qualifier, Peter Gojowczyk, at the China Open, then blasted the choice of tennis balls at the tournament.
